CommentBody:
I researched the deleted groups in the ADInventoy_GroupView and discovered that the group exists. Still, the IsDeleted checkbox was unchecked, which means the ADI doesn't have access to the deleted object from your domain controller.
Â 
I advised the customer to log in to his domain controller with the service account, open the Active Directory Administrative Center, select his domain, and click the Deleted Object. 
If it's not listed, the customer has to enable it.
